<br>
basically it's this:<br>
<br>
1) Don't harass each other. If anyone here is attacked on the basis of race, religion, sexual orientation or artistic skills..the aggressor will be toasted.<br>
<br>
2) Don't steal or take credit for work you didn't do. If you copy something..give full credit to the source material. Failure to do so will result in hazing.<br>
<br>
3) Don't have giant personal icons and signatures. Aside from being slow loading it's also an eyesore. My sites not here so you can have a billboard to YOUR site. Don't get me wrong..you can have links or buttons to your site in your sig..just don't have a banner or large graphic...thats plain obnoxious.<br>
<br>
4) The rules on the BBS apply in the chatroom. If you act like an ass in there you will be banned from here.<br>
<br>
5) Don't post anything inappropriate. Nudity is fine (yes, I'm allowing nudity) but if it involves a sex act or torture you will be smacked down. No Hentai...no Pervy stuff. Try and keep Gore to a minimum too..there are kids here for cryin' out load. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Edit: If you want to post an image containing nudity or excessive violence, please put <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> a warning in the subject line</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> AND <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> link your image (ie do not use the image tag)</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
6) No warez, cracks, hacks or illegal stuff. This means no posting stuff that has to do with downloading a program for free that would normally cost money.<br>
<br>
7) Don't bump your threads or spam the board. If you need a definition of &quot;Spamming&quot; ask a mod.<br>
